 Zhou Siyue!

33
00:03:00,290 --> 00:03:03,470
 Zhou Siyue! I'm here for you!

34
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:07,500
Zhou Siyue!

35
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:10,800
Ding Xian!

36
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:17,740
Zhou Siyue, it's so nice to see you.

37
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:32,040
You never picked up my call or returned my message.

38
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:35,000
I thought you wouldn't come out to see me.

39
00:04:42,410 --> 00:04:45,400
I just have something to say.

40
00:04:48,060 --> 00:04:49,760
Tell me.

41
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:54,450
I like you.

42
00:04:56,010 --> 00:04:58,670
Have you ever felt the same?

43
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:09,520
Ding Xian,

44
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:14,130
I have no plans for romantic relationships now.

45
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:20,430
It's getting late. You should go back.

46
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:25,820
Focus on your studying and don't come looking for me again.

47
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:38,470
We said that we would get into Huaqing together.

48
00:05:38,470 --> 00:05:40,760
Now I have done it.

49
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:45,480
I just want to know if you ever had feelings for me.

50
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:49,170
Is the answer...

51
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,990
really important?

52
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,990
Ding Xian,

53
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:04,770
we all have our own lives.

54
00:06:04,780 --> 00:06:06,681
So what?

55
00:06:29,850 --> 00:06:31,750
Zhou Siyue!

56
00:06:35,410 --> 00:06:37,750
Do you know my secret?

57
00:06:46,476 --> 00:06:48,856
It's getting late. I'm going to leave now.

