63
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:20,720
 It was August 2009.

64
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:24,280
 Summer in the south is scorching hot.

65
00:08:24,970 --> 00:08:29,490
 We left the small town of Keshan and moved to Shenhai.

66
00:08:30,170 --> 00:08:34,060
 Everything we passed by was so strange.

67
00:08:36,450 --> 00:08:39,460
 It was a whole new beginning.

68
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:43,220
 I hoped the city of Shenhai can treat me nicely.

69
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:49,340
 I hoped I could maintain my performance at school this semester and make some new friends.

70
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:53,080
 And I hoped everything could go well.

71
00:08:55,110 --> 00:08:57,110
- Sir, take it easy.
 - Be careful with the cabinet.

72
00:08:57,110 --> 00:08:59,080
Come on, over here.

73
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:06,540
Xian, here are your books. Put them away.

74
00:09:14,582 --> 00:09:17,226
Siyue! Siyue!

75
00:09:17,226 --> 00:09:19,340
Your keys!

76
00:09:20,414 --> 00:09:22,848
Can you be lazier?

77
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:26,515
- Brother, what's going on?
 - I twisted my ankle.

78
00:09:26,515 --> 00:09:27,660
What are you staring at?

79
00:09:27,660 --> 00:09:30,640
Go move the things. Stop wasting time.

80
00:09:32,450 --> 00:09:34,540
Ding Juncong.

81
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:49,300
- This place is huge.
 - Don't waste any time.

82
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:52,010
We have to go out later.

83
00:09:52,910 --> 00:09:55,710
Refrigerator... Yes, put it against the wall.

84
00:09:56,980 --> 00:09:59,500
Put the other things in the second bedroom.

85
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:02,164
Juncong. Xian. You two are sharing one bedroom.

86
00:10:02,164 --> 00:10:04,020
- No way!
 - No way!

87
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:07,810
I'm old enough now. I'm not sharing a room with him.

88
00:10:07,810 --> 00:10:09,320
How about I go stay at school?

89
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,220
Why would you do that?

90
00:10:11,220 --> 00:10:13,690
With such a good apartment, you want to waste money on that?

91
00:10:13,690 --> 00:10:15,210
Do you think we have cash just lying around?

92
00:10:15,210 --> 00:10:16,811
All right.

93
00:10:16,811 --> 00:10:18,230
We have another small room.

94
00:10:18,230 --> 00:10:20,700
I could give up my study room and make it their bedroom.

95
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:21,810
How's that, Wanxian?

96
00:10:21,810 --> 00:10:24,510
- Fine. You two pick your rooms.
 - Great!

97
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:27,571
- Take it easy.
 - I'm taking this room.

98
00:10:27,571 --> 00:10:29,865
I want this room, too.

99
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,350
Ding Juncong, why did you push me?

100
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:34,810
Mom! Mom! Mom!

101
00:10:34,810 --> 00:10:35,800
What are you doing?

102
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:38,240
What are you doing? You...

103
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,341
Apologize!

104
00:10:40,341 --> 00:10:41,550
I'm not going to!

105
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:43,260
That's fine, but you have to let me have this room.

106
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,370
No way!

107
00:10:44,370 --> 00:10:46,810
What does a little kid like you need such a big room for?

108
00:10:46,810 --> 00:10:49,590
I don't care. I want that room! That is the room I want!

109
00:10:49,590 --> 00:10:52,830
Xian, you are the elder one, can you let your brother choose first?

110
00:10:52,830 --> 00:10:54,550
- Mom!
 - Wanxian, where is my medicine kit?

111
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:56,200
I don't know, look for it yourself.

112
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,892
You...

113
00:10:57,892 --> 00:11:00,092
Why is the medicine kit missing?

114
00:11:05,050 --> 00:11:08,660
- Xianxian, are you all right?
 - Yes.

115
00:11:08,660 --> 00:11:10,080
Then hurry up.

116
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:12,610
The Zhous are waiting for us.

117
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,653
I don't want to go.

118
00:11:14,653 --> 00:11:16,893
Stop nagging and hurry up.

119
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,750
Coming!

120
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,970
- Zhou!
 - Wencheng!

121
00:11:29,970 --> 00:11:31,540
You are finally here.

122
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,824
Come on, get in.

123
00:11:32,824 --> 00:11:33,961
Say hello to Uncle Zhou.

124
00:11:33,961 --> 00:11:35,590
- No need to change into slippers.
 - Hello, Uncle.

125
00:11:35,590 --> 00:11:38,050
- It's okay.
 - We should change. Look at the floor.

126
00:11:38,050 --> 00:11:39,130
This is...

127
00:11:39,130 --> 00:11:40,980
Sorry to bother you about the school.

128
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:42,780
It's just a little thank-you gift.

129
00:11:42,780 --> 00:11:44,280
You are being a stranger right now.

130
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:45,970
I'll leave it here.

131
00:11:45,970 --> 00:11:47,200
It's okay, come in. This is...

132
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,520
Jinyun.

133
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:50,220
Wencheng is here.

134
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:53,650
- Hello!
 - That's a lot of work you've done.

135
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:55,340
- Nice to see you.
 - Nice to see you.

136
00:11:55,340 --> 00:11:58,440
Ding. Wanxian. Welcome.

137
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:01,740
This is Auntie Li who I brought up all the time.

138
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:03,570
 Sorry, Auntie Li.

139
00:12:03,570 --> 00:12:05,740
 The truth is my mom never mentioned you.

140
00:12:05,740 --> 00:12:09,230
I always wanted to bring Xian here to see you.

141
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:10,429
Am I right?

142
00:12:10,429 --> 00:12:11,960
 One of the signatures of teenagers.

143
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:14,130
 Lying without feeling guilty at all.

144
00:12:14,130 --> 00:12:16,010
Auntie Li, hello.

145
00:12:16,010 --> 00:12:17,880
I heard a lot about you from my mom.

146
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:20,000
- You are a nice kid.
 - Wencheng, sit.

147
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,900
Yes. Don't just stand here. Let's sit and eat.

148
00:12:21,900 --> 00:12:24,000
Okay. Change your shoes.

149
00:12:24,537 --> 00:12:26,170
Your dad and Uncle Zhou have been friends since childhood.

150
00:12:26,170 --> 00:12:28,690
Uncle Zhou got this job in Shenhai for your dad.

151
00:12:28,690 --> 00:12:31,240
You two, behave here.

152
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:34,810
Before you guys arrived, I was telling Yun

153
00:12:34,810 --> 00:12:36,570
- that we haven't met for some time.
 - Sit.

154
00:12:36,570 --> 00:12:38,350
We are drinking tonight.

155
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:39,610
Yeah, we have to drink.

156
00:12:39,610 --> 00:12:40,560
- Hurry up.
 - You have no objection, do you?

157
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:42,370
- Not at all.
 - Why don't you also have some?

158
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:43,970
Sure. Thank you.

159
00:12:44,780 --> 00:12:47,110
They are Siyue's schoolmates.

160
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:48,740
They are here to play games together.

161
00:12:48,740 --> 00:12:50,160
- Hello, Uncle and Auntie.
 - Hello.

162
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:52,050
Where is Siyue?

163
00:12:52,050 --> 00:12:53,146
He's asleep.

164
00:12:53,146 --> 00:12:54,470
Ask him to come out.

165
00:12:54,470 --> 00:12:56,648
Master Zhou, wake up.

166
00:12:56,648 --> 00:12:57,640
Your mom is asking you to join us at the dining table.

167
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:58,760
 Coming.

168
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:00,490
Going to school nowadays is rough.

169
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:01,960
What a crowd!

170
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:05,361
Siyue! Come and say "hi" to Uncle Ding and Auntie Ye.

171
00:13:05,361 --> 00:13:06,880
Uncle Ding. Auntie Ye.

172
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,200
You are all grown up.

173
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,510
- I'm sorry about that.
 - There's no need to be shy. Come.

174
00:13:10,510 --> 00:13:12,570
We haven't met for years.

175
00:13:12,570 --> 00:13:13,790
Let's cheer for this reunion.

176
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:15,250
Right. Welcome.

177
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:16,760
- Thank you.
 - Sorry for the trouble.

178
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:18,120
It's not easy to prepare for this.

179
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:21,250
Have some food.

180
00:13:21,710 --> 00:13:24,440
Xianxian, you should remember.

181
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:27,640
This is Siyue. You met when you were younger.

182
00:13:28,610 --> 00:13:31,570
Siyue looks so handsome now.

183
00:13:31,570 --> 00:13:34,740
He's all grown up.

184
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:38,150
I held you in my arms when you were little.

185
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:39,453
How time flies.

186
00:13:39,453 --> 00:13:41,370
You don't say!

187
00:13:41,370 --> 00:13:43,530
He's already in high school now.

188
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:45,130
Right, Xianxian.

189
00:13:45,130 --> 00:13:48,880
I heard that you performed well on the high school entrance exam.

190
00:13:49,930 --> 00:13:52,006
I got 695.

191
00:13:52,006 --> 00:13:54,306
That's impressive.

192
00:13:57,240 --> 00:13:59,220
That's not my best.

193
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:03,540
Our Xianxian would study until 2:00 a.m. before exams.

194
00:14:03,540 --> 00:14:04,610
She can't be persuaded.

195
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:07,710
She just loves school so much.

196
00:14:09,180 --> 00:14:12,050
Siyue, what was your score?

197
00:14:12,660 --> 00:14:14,760
Me?

198
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:16,576
680.

199
00:14:17,060 --> 00:14:19,132
Just past the line.

200
00:14:19,132 --> 00:14:20,710
Siyue is talented.

201
00:14:20,710 --> 00:14:23,150
He passed the line easily.

202
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:25,030
We were playing games before the exam.

203
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,740
You are also Siyue's classmate, right?

204
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,740
What was your score?

205
00:14:31,987 --> 00:14:33,300
Auntie,

206
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:35,690
the score only needs to meet the line.

207
00:14:35,690 --> 00:14:37,340
That's what I've been saying to Xianxian.

208
00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:39,520
The score only needs to meet the line.

209
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:43,760
But Xianxian just loves to study. She's a tough person.

210
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:45,740
Enough. Stop talking and eat your food.

211
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:47,690
Xian is clearly a nice kid.

212
00:14:47,690 --> 00:14:49,570
She will achieve something in the future.

213
00:14:49,570 --> 00:14:52,460
- You did a good job bringing her up, Ding.
 - That's not true. You are flattering me.

214
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:54,860
- I should learn from you.
 - Learn from me?

215
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:56,340
We should learn from each other.

216
00:14:56,340 --> 00:15:00,950
Yeah. Xian never makes me worry when it comes to studying.

217
00:15:01,470 --> 00:15:02,540
Siyue!

218
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:06,409
You should discuss school-related questions together.

219
00:15:06,409 --> 00:15:08,379
Xianxian knows everything.

220
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,766
Sure, Auntie.

221
00:15:10,766 --> 00:15:13,110
- I will.
 - This is great.

222
00:15:13,110 --> 00:15:16,550
You two should communicate more.

223
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:20,270
Your grandfathers arranged your marriage when you were little.

224
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:25,600
Why bring that up?

225
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,220
That's where we were at.

226
00:15:27,220 --> 00:15:29,253
That's true.

227
00:15:29,253 --> 00:15:33,680
But it's too early for them to think about that.

228
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:35,110
They are just high schoolers.

229
00:15:35,110 --> 00:15:36,200
Yes. That's right.

230
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,450
Studying should be your focus now.

231
00:15:37,450 --> 00:15:38,976
Come on.

232
00:15:38,976 --> 00:15:40,866
How do we cancel the marriage?

233
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:45,496
Nonsense. Auntie Ye was just kidding. Did you take it seriously?

234
00:15:45,496 --> 00:15:46,996
That's right.

235
00:15:47,570 --> 00:15:50,232
I'm kidding with Auntie, too.

236
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:53,200
- Come on.
 - He's a funny kid.

237
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:55,573
 Like I would like you.

238
00:15:57,150 --> 00:15:59,379
Uncle Ding. Auntie Ye. Please make yourselves at home.

239
00:15:59,379 --> 00:16:00,960
I'm finished.

240
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,150
That's all you need?

241
00:16:02,150 --> 00:16:04,120
I had too much in the morning. Don't mind me.

242
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:06,280
I... I'm finished, too.

243
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:07,635
Me, too.

244
00:16:07,635 --> 00:16:08,900
Come on, ignore them.

245
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:10,760
- Here.
 - Sorry about that.

246
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:13,930
Boys at their age are a little rebellious.

247
00:16:13,930 --> 00:16:15,640
- That's right.
 - Our kids are the same.

248
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:18,400
Yeah. That's how all of them are.

249
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:20,050
Sister, I need to use the bathroom.

250
00:16:20,050 --> 00:16:22,340
Okay. I'll take you.

251
00:16:26,370 --> 00:16:28,742
 I got 695.

252
00:16:28,742 --> 00:16:32,270
 Xianxian is such a sensitive kid.

253
00:16:32,270 --> 00:16:34,300
 I never have to worry about her.

254
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:36,640
Xianxian knows everything.

255
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:39,310
Her mom was trying to be Siyue's in-law.

256
00:16:39,310 --> 00:16:41,250
 Who would arrange marriage nowadays?

257
00:16:41,250 --> 00:16:43,700
 Yeah, that must be a joke.

258
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:45,540
Did you guys see the bump on her head?

259
00:16:45,540 --> 00:16:47,250
Doesn't it look like a horn?

260
00:16:47,250 --> 00:16:49,570
She was trying to cover it like we wouldn't notice.

261
00:16:49,570 --> 00:16:51,810
She's like Shrek.

262
00:16:51,810 --> 00:16:53,750
The green monster.

263
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:55,810
And what was his wife's name?

264
00:16:55,810 --> 00:16:56,933
Fiona!

265
00:16:56,933 --> 00:16:58,440
- Fiona!
