 - What do you want, Song Ziqi!

514
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:26,630
Why can't I get rid of you?

515
00:30:27,192 --> 00:30:30,270
Like I want to be sitting by your side.

516
00:30:35,610 --> 00:30:38,420
